name: AmbientWindSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open ambient wind sounds”
”Alexa ask ambient wind sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ambient wind sounds
des: Let the sounds of an ambient wind blowing outside thrust you into a deep sleep. Ambient Wind Sounds is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. \n\nAll you need to do is say Alexa start Ambient Wind Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
